Separation of concerns
ShortCodes → core business entity (URL mapping)
RateLimits → infrastructure concern (throttling / quota)


If URL is inactive for 7 days, remove it from db and give alert to user.


RATE LIMITING

On clicking the button, create short URL. System will check if a user email is coming from a form or not. If not, it's the IP based rate limiting.If yes, it's the user based rate limiting. IP willbe a non null valuebut user can be a null value.

dual-key rate limiting strategy:

Registered user → key = email
Anonymous user → key = IP address

